Experimental Tracing JIT VM for Guile
=====================================

About
-----

This directory contains modules for JIT compiling traced bytecode
instructions. Currently works under x86-64 architecture only.


Requirements
------------

* Requirements for Guile
* [GNU lightning][https://www.gnu.org/software/lightning/]


Building
--------

From top level directory:

> ./autogen.sh
> ./configure --enable-lightning
> make


Usage
-----

To run a script with tracing JIT VM:

> guile --tjit file.scm

To start REPL with tracing JIT VM:

> guile --tjit
